author: dlr
msg: Fix compilation warnings, which trigger a build failure when building
with EXTRA_CFLAGS='-Wall -Werror' using GCC 4.0.1 (on Fedora Core 4).
(Notify2::onNotify): Change parameter name from notify to wcNotify
to avoid shadowing method of the same name.
(Inputer::read): Cast apr_size_t to jint to avoid complaint about
comparsion between signed and unsigned integers.
Added newline to end of file.

author: dlr
msg: (SVNClient::blame): Fix bug where the return value of
svn_client_blame2() was being captured, but never used.

author: maxb
msg: Make the Python bindings automatically support the SVN_ASP_DOT_NET_HACK.
